Package: moonycode-dev
Version: @VERSION@
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17)
Maintainer: Andrey Kovalenko aka Keva <keva@rambler.ru>
Description: moonycode - fast and tiny cyrillic codepages and unicode support
  This package contains codepages convertors and decoders static library and headers for most popular
  cyrillic codepages: 1251, 866, koi8, utf-8, utf-16 and utf-32.
